<p><ent>Sick</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Sick
<hw>Sick</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To fall sick; to sicken.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sick-brained</ent>⟦br⟧
